data.title: Your “Stand Up And Cheer!!!” Friday Evening Open Thread – [DOOR FLIES OPEN]
data.text:
It’s the first weekend of NCAA Football…2019 version.

Several games have already been played. Clemson rolled over GT, as expected. I hate those asshats. Minny barely got past San Diego State. Utah got away with a big win versus the other Mormon bunch. And UCF posted 62 up on….shit, what’s the name of that shitty school they played?

Meh, who cares? They suck.

But as always, we’re doing Cheerleaders this week. (so to speak).

This week it’s college Cheerleaders. Next week….its the Pros.

–

Sports To Make You Cheer 2Nite

NCAA Football

Rice @ Army – 6:00pmEDT – TV: CBSSN

(19)Wisconsin @ South Florida – 7:00pmEDT – TV: ESPN

Tulsa @ (18)Michigan State – 7:00pmEDT – TV: FS1

UMass @ Rutgers – 7:15pmEDT – TV: B1GN

Utah State @ Wake Forest – 8:00pmEDT – TV: ACCN

Purdue @ Nevada – 9:30pmEDT – TV: CBSSN

ColorAdo State @ ColorAdo – 10:00pmEDT – TV: ESPN

Okie State @ Oregon State – 10:30pmEDT – TV: FS1

Full Weekend Schedule

MLB

Oakland @ NYY – 7:00pmEDT – TV: MLBN (regional split)

Cleveland @ Tampa Bay – 7:00pmEDT – TV: MLBN (regional split)

Full Schedule

And there’s other crappy stuff on but screw it.

–

Cheerleaders, Baby!!!!!!

Yes, I’ve told the story of being with two Cheerleaders at once before.

I WILL NOT REPEAT MYSELF!!!!!

(But it was a fun coupla months)

Enjoy….

Oh stop it. You knew I was gonna finish with an NC State girl.

You’re going down this weekend, ECU.

He says that like it’s a bad thing.

(hehehehehe)

Have a nice weekend everyone.

Love ya’s.

–
